{
  "id": "RAW_46344d46",
  "title": "Wan2.2-Animate 又火了，5 分钟让抠脚大汉秒变高冷女神。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647676062&idx=1&sn=e0580fe50738aa90778f9e1b02070d49",
  "date": "2025-10-30 01:31:00",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最近，一个视频在推上传疯了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一张美女照片，加上一条自己录制的视频，就能生成一张极其自然的换脸视频，表情和动作复刻的都很好。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而它用到的，就是阿里家的开源模型，Wan2.2 Animate。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">其实Wan2.2 Animate一个月前杠发布的时候就火过一波，不知道你们对这个宅男变身女主播的视频眼熟不，当时我刷到了n次。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500192361\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1797235023041475\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"651\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"651\" data-height=\"768\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"663\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=19a6575f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpfGqXJOaPRtwy6f2cECjMAIwdRNQT3yLQeTewNUy6WEOk4u9JOmicIWywet1WM8JEjqIC3NsPuibRg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后你会发现，这次再火起来，流量密码依然没变。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">搞颜色还是第一生产力。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但你们都知道，一个模型，它能搞颜色，不代表它只能搞颜色。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">相反，很可能意味着它上限很高。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">毕竟在座的各位都是老司机，阅历惊人，出来的效果如果哪里不自然，大概率一眼就看得出来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">至于效果，直接给大家看看，我用我自己的视频加上不同角色的图片，做出来的效果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">更复杂的表情，它也能复刻。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">由于我自己确实是个不爱拍照的I人，表情没那么丰富，这里借用听泉老师代为出镜一下。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">再加上一个美女。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500192362\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3333333333333333\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1666\" data-height=\"2221\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5a57821f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURpfGqXJOaPRtwy6f2cECjMABS4tCRGR2Pds3J9TmeyrBIrmaxbLJ9A7rHMgzDztJUgufJnKBH7D7Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">出来的效果是这样的。表情模仿确实很到位，就是感觉高冷美女一下子变成东北银了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500192374\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"320\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"320\" data-backh=\"240\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=58e41428&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FOjgKEXmLURpfGqXJOaPRtwy6f2cECjMAbum3D8aguTyGOaB9BjaqkwAAogytuBZswXA2QE8CvhUPPq7BsvNaoA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">想得到更逼真的效果呢，还可以变声线。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">直接做一条声音来替换就行，海螺+剪映就可以实现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这样就能同时替换形象和声音了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我用海螺做了声音，出来的效果是这样的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你也很难想象这个视频的背后是一个我这样的糙老爷们对不对。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以，不多说什么了，朋友们，网恋有风险，奔现需谨慎。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">万幸的是，现在的Wan2.2 Animate</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还不能做到实时输出，否则你想一下，假设以后郭老师，良子这些人也能当颜值主播开直播了，那会是一个怎样的世界。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当然了，类似于这种在违法边缘疯狂大鹏展翅的事情，我不会干，而且我也，绝对绝对，不希望任何人这么干。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不过话说回来，如果你的诉求就只是想给自己整一些小哥哥小姐姐的舞蹈视频看，用它还是很方便的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也可以拉一个你喜欢的角色来复刻跳舞，比mmd方便多了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">动作表情啥的都挺到位的，但也有个问题，就是，一旦手部动作多了，手指还是很容易崩坏。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个问题目前比较无解，很难顶。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">除了跳舞之外，还可以做一些影视二创。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如，让赵本山出演《了不起的盖茨比》，还原小李子经典镜头。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Welcome to 乡村大舞台，有梦你就来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还有这个经典的梗，接着奏乐接着舞，可以直接换了一个人来演。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当然，我推荐这个模型的原因不只是因为效果好。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">类似的东西去年就有了，Runway，Viggle，都能实现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但问题是，这些模型都不开源。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">像Wan2.2 Animate</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这样一直走在开源路上的，已经不多了。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">想玩这个模型，最简单的方法就是去通义万相官网，网址在这里：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://tongyi.aliyun.com/wan/explore\" target=\"_blank\">https://tongyi.aliyun.com/wan/explore</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">进去之后在底部这里，找到数字人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500192360\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.26666666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"840\" data-width=\"840\" data-height=\"224\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=49ca87e2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpfGqXJOaPRtwy6f2cECjMAxmkHFicpD5JWWfickqgjfzWDXGcDgQehJ3fIQI0DzFibVZ2HW8qkicKL8g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后选择角色替换或者动作模仿，选择专业模式输出，再上传参考图和参考视频，就OK了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500192359\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2799043062200957\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"836\" data-width=\"836\" data-height=\"234\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ef1f6a84&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpfGqXJOaPRtwy6f2cECjMArR27OWNmckIN89s6MU8CQ7t5Re480QZVyS4axK7MtUWd1jyx33MIqw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">简单说一下动作模仿和角色替换的区别。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">假设我们现在有一张参考图A，主体为A，背景为A，一个参考视频B，主体为B，背景为B。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">动作模仿就是，主体A在背景A里，做着主体B的动作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也就是让参考图动起来，模仿视频中的动作和表情。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">角色替换则是，主体A在背景B里，做主体B的动作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就是保留原视频的背景环境，用参考图中的角色替换视频中的角色。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这里面还有一个小技巧，就是，如果想要达到开头case那种只换脸不换背景的效果，可以多加一个流程：在视频中截一帧，用这一帧图和角色图，在seedream或者nano banana上，生成一张和视频中背景完全一致的图，把这张图作为生成视频的参考图。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">举个例子，这张拼图的左边，是我从视频里截的一帧，右边是我生成的用于替换我自己的角色图。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500192367\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42685185185185187\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"4590\" data-height=\"1959\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c7847a55&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURpfGqXJOaPRtwy6f2cECjMAAyh1Ed0QDmuQAuoSeNFwI0H3HxWiamVaptg8ulHS9N7jVgYd9wk8X3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后我用即梦，生成了一张和视频中背景一致的图，长这样。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500192366\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2560\" data-height=\"1440\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0733a8ff&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURpfGqXJOaPRtwy6f2cECjMA7DfwNuYKgia4AzdyNhrTuwIocgwWRF6zEVGsDoIFO7rRdQhbRo9z1vQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最后把这张图放进去跑case，出来的就是一张，和原背景一模一样的换脸视频了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500192364\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5037837837837837\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"925\" data-width=\"925\" data-height=\"466\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9ff0d16e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpfGqXJOaPRtwy6f2cECjMAKvoQbl7ms6C1flG4Qj5E256hx3eIticnPH6XLGhd6iaxBjGCz9qCgj4Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">有了这些输入，你基本上就可以愉快地开始玩耍了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果你想进行本地部署的话，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;1 1 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Wan2.2 Animate也完全开源了：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/Wan-Video/Wan2.2\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Wan-Video/Wan2.2</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500192409\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.32432432432432434\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"518\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"518\" data-backh=\"168\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=53c1d5ce&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpfGqXJOaPRtwy6f2cECjMA2wn6oYKsqQ3LMxIYXh4icc6YKfK8gLpBmbJFSTGtseIWAOrmphEibgIg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">目前也支持了ComfyUI。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">从技术的角度看，Wan2.2 Animate的意义，绝对是积极的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它把过去需要昂贵动捕设备、专业动画师才能实现的表情和动作捕捉，变成了一个普通人点几下鼠标就能完成的事情。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而且，是开源的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这也意味着，真的可以进入到企业、剧组里，进行私有化部署，来做很多的实际效果。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这也意味着很多独立动画师，可以用极低的成本，让自己的角色活起来。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">更意味着电影制作，可以在特效、数字替身、甚至虚拟演员这些领域，打开全新的想象空间。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">要知道，专业动捕真的很贵的。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而且，除了用</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;1 1 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 16px; margin-right: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Wan2.2 Animate来去做角色替换之外，还有一些其他的流程，也是很好玩的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;1 1 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 16px; margin-right: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如，我的好基友</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">@GongWangG</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，在组里用</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Wan2.1-Vace，玩的实验小demo，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Wan2.2 Animate不是做角色替换嘛，但用</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Wan2.1-Vace</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，也可以用来保持角色一致性，但更改掉整个背景做实拍合成VFX。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这种流程，也是非常酷的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">未来我们也许能看到已经逝去的演员，在新电影里“复活”，用AI完美复刻他们的音容笑貌和表演风格，也许也能看到很多经典的场景被复刻出现，而我们就在其中畅游。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这在技术上，已经不再是科幻。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它降低了创作的门槛，解放了生产力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">凡事，就怕这个但是。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这些技术，同样可以，毫不费力地，割开我们现实世界的信任基石。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就说一个最实际的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你在网上看到一段视频，某个公众人物，说着极其出格的话，做着极其不齿的事，视频看起来天衣无缝，没有任何破绽，你信不信？</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以我说，我之前还犹豫了一下，要不要写这篇文章。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但想了想，最后还是决定写出来了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们理应看见它的好，也看见它的坏。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">技术永远是中立的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它就像火，可以取暖，也可以焚城。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但真正重要的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">是那群握着火把的人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我相信，我们还是一群。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">用火取暖的人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:var(--articleFontsize);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><strong style=\"white-space-collapse:preserve;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\">以上，既然看到这里了，如果觉得不错，随手点个赞、在看、转发三连吧，如果想第一时间收到推送，也可以给我个星标⭐～谢谢你看我的文章，我们，下次再见。</span></span></strong></strong></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"text-wrap:wrap;outline:0px;color:rgb(178, 178, 178);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:12px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-style:solid;text-decoration-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 作者：卡兹克、水杉</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 投稿或爆料，请联系邮箱：</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">wzglyay@virxact.com</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章详细介绍了阿里开源 AI 模型 Wan2.2 Animate，展示其高质量视频换脸与动作复刻能力及多种应用场景，并探讨技术伦理。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章详细介绍了阿里开源 AI 模型 Wan2.2 Animate，展示其高质量视频换脸与动作复刻能力及多种应用场景，并探讨技术伦理。",
  "summary": "文章深入介绍了阿里巴巴开源的 AI 模型 Wan2.2 Animate，该模型能够通过一张参考图片和一段驱动视频，生成表情和动作高度自然的换脸或动作复刻视频。作者通过多个生动实例展示了其在复刻复杂表情和动作方面的出色效果，并指出其在降低专业动捕门槛、推动内容创作（如舞蹈视频制作、影视二创、数字替身）方面的巨大潜力，尤其强调了其开源的重大意义。尽管模型在表情和动作复刻方面表现出色，但在处理复杂手部动作时仍存在手指容易崩坏的局限性。文章提供了通义万相官网的在线使用入口、具体操作步骤以及本地部署的 GitHub 链接，极大地方便了用户上手实践。同时，作者也深入探讨了该技术可能带来的伦理风险，如制造虚假信息，呼吁使用者审慎并负责任地对待技术，体现了对技术双面性的深刻思考。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Wan2.2 Animate 是一款开源的 AI 视频生成模型，能实现高质量的换脸和动作复刻。",
      "explanation": "该模型通过结合参考图和视频，生成表情动作自然的视频，极大降低了传统动捕的门槛，且效果逼真，具备广泛应用潜力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "模型支持多种创意应用场景，包括舞蹈视频制作、影视二创及数字替身。",
      "explanation": "除了娱乐用途，该模型在电影制作、独立动画创作等专业领域也有巨大价值，能有效降低创作成本，拓展创作边界。"
    },
    {
      "point": "文章强调技术开源的积极意义，并探讨了 AI 技术带来的潜在伦理风险。",
      "explanation": "开源加速了技术普及与创新，但同时技术滥用可能损害社会信任，作者呼吁使用者审慎并负责任地对待技术。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
